Package: MALDIassist
Title: Mathematical Utilities for MALDI-TOF Mass Spectrometry
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Wonseok", "Oh", , "125277369+hiows@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-0687-8466"))
Description: Tools for MALDI-TOF mass spectrometry workflows in R, covering the
    path from raw Bruker spectra to a cohort-level peak matrix. Includes loading
    of Bruker spectra, smoothing and baseline correction, Gaussian
    kernel-density-based peak detection (including shoulder peaks), peak-quality
    metrics and filtering, and cohort feature analysis. Performance-critical
    routines are implemented in C++ via 'Rcpp'.
